column_description: A unique identifier for each student, serving as the primary key
A foreign key referencing the `address_id` in the `Addresses` table, indicating the student's current residential address
A foreign key referencing the `address_id` in the `Addresses` table, indicating the student's permanent residential address
The first name of the student
The middle name of the student, if applicable
The last name of the student
The student's mobile or cell phone number
The student's email address for communication
The student's Social Security Number or equivalent identification number
The date and time when the student first registered at the institution
The date and time when the student left the institution, if applicable
Additional details or notes about the student, if any
